{"tid":2121803,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"睇返轉頭達哥真係好冤枉","createTime":"2020-07-23T14:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T15:27:11.000Z","uid":57911,"like":19,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa06d12c10990fcc8cd3dd177ad93ebfcc7d2a5","tid":2121803,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:20:11.000Z","msg":"人哋藍嘅俾粉絲離棄都算<br />\n達哥擺明係黃<br />\nig有貼721831都俾人帶風向鬧到狗咁<br />\n達哥心態爆炸又冇人想諒解佢<br />\n仲更加俾人小題大做砌佢獲甘<br />\n<br />\n我知大家睇開達哥對佢不滿都唔係第一日嘅事<br />\n但係俾啲風向撚小事化大係唔係onL9<br />\n又唔係大奸大惡<br />\n大家當期時仲面臨大敵<br />\n有咁多時間搞達哥點解唔檢討下點做先好<br />\n<br />\n睇到依度覺唔覺得自己有少少對唔住達哥對唔住手足"},{"pid":"9c5106e62d32031f812e1da397dfae435d11115a","tid":2121803,"uid":66260,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:22:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fdaf55429756afb238e4928ac46f5b11a44c472d","tid":2121803,"uid":52558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:23:27.000Z","msg":"依個世界邊個冇俾兒登仔屌過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d46ea2e758c8f4189026c9f2bb85ca5fbee728","tid":2121803,"uid":256952,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:23:38.000Z","msg":"永遠支持達哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217c84343891fefc04019d99ca007bb30bc5258c","tid":2121803,"uid":59976,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oXygGhX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXygGhX.jpg&h=016c84d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8624e34da5682173ce74ade4f482e6696169de25","tid":2121803,"uid":37666,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T15:20:08.000Z","msg":"我係大陸最好你地個個都反<br />\n鬥到無人黃就最開心"},{"pid":"9037072cba270998f08cfedad824c69e63886156","tid":2121803,"uid":69064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T15: